        "body": "\n\n    <div id=\"alarmik-top\" class=\"text-center\">\n\n    \t<div class=\"text-center\">\n        \t<img src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik-realpixels.png\" class=\"realpx-iphone\"/>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n\t    <span data-picture data-alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\" class=\"maxwidth\">\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik4-small.png\"></span>\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik4.png\" data-media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"></span>\n\t        <noscript>\n\t            <img src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik4.png\" alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\">\n\t        </noscript>\n\t    </span>\n\n\t    <span data-picture data-alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\" class=\"maxwidth\">\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik5-small.png\"></span>\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik5.png\" data-media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"></span>\n\t        <noscript>\n\t            <img src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik5.png\" alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\">\n\t        </noscript>\n\t    </span>\n\n\t    <span data-picture data-alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\" class=\"maxwidth\">\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik6-small.png\"></span>\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik6.png\" data-media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"></span>\n\t        <noscript>\n\t            <img src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik6.png\" alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\">\n\t        </noscript>\n\t    </span>\n\n\t    <span data-picture data-alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\" class=\"maxwidth\">\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik7-small.png\"></span>\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik7.png\" data-media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"></span>\n\t        <noscript>\n\t            <img src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik7.png\" alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\">\n\t        </noscript>\n\t    </span>\n\n\t    <span data-picture data-alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\" class=\"maxwidth\">\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik8-small.png\"></span>\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik8.png\" data-media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"></span>\n\t        <noscript>\n\t            <img src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik8.png\" alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\">\n\t        </noscript>\n\t    </span>\n\n\t    <span data-picture data-alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\" class=\"maxwidth\">\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik3-small.png\"></span>\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik3.png\" data-media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"></span>\n\t        <noscript>\n\t            <img src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik3.png\" alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\">\n\t        </noscript>\n\t    </span>\n\n\t    <span data-picture data-alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\" class=\"maxwidth\">\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik2-small.png\"></span>\n\t        <span data-src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik2.png\" data-media=\"(min-width: 480px)\"></span>\n\t        <noscript>\n\t            <img src=\"../assets/projects/alarmik2.png\" alt=\"Alarmik for iPhone\">\n\t        </noscript>\n\t    </span>\n      \n    </div>\n\n\t<div id=\"alarmik-bottom\">\n\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"large-12 columns\">\n\n\t\t\t    <h2>Project Info</h2>\n\n\t\t\t\t<dl class=\"project-details\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<dt>Client</dt>\n\t\t\t\t\t<dd>Personal</dd>\n\t\t\t\t\t<dt>Responsible for</dt>\n\t\t\t\t\t<dd>Idea, Design, Development</dd>\n\t\t\t\t\t<dt>Type</dt>\n\t\t\t\t\t<dd>iPhone App</dd>\n\t\t\t\t</dl>\n\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"large-12 columns\">\n\n\t\t\t    <h2>Status</h2>\n\n\t\t\t    <p>\n\t\t\t      \tAlarmik is a concept I've been exploring since January 2013. One of the reasons I've been holding off development for a while is that as of right now it's still not possible to set a real alarm in iOS7. You can only play a sound that ignores the 'silent switch' of the iPhone if your app is running in the background. I hope Apple will give us access to setting an actual alarm in the future so third party alarm clock apps don't need to give the user a big set of instructions to set an alarm that will actually wake them in the morning..\n\t\t\t    </p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t</div>\n\n",
